

=Bio=

Founder of [http://JOLOCOM.com JOLOCOM], that develops the [[Social_Dynamic_Graph|Social Dynamic Graph]], a graphical interface of a mobile P2P Network application that connects People, Ideas, Projects, Skills, Places, Things & facilitates P2P ValueXchange ([[Open_Value_Network|Open Value Network]]).

[http://JOLOCOM.com JOLOCOM] wishes to be an instrument of P2P collaboration and interaction in a collaborative society that promotes the integration of our immediate and indirect environments... including our personal relations, nature, food, things and cultural roots.


